reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly what I wanted.
reviews.reviewText: It's exactly what I wanted, extra clicky clacky, round key caps that make it hard to accidentally hit an adjacent key along with the one you are trying to hit. The multitude of rainbow effects are gorgeous, though you can't seem to just choose one single color, it's all or none with this keyboard, but I'm OK with that.It's compatible with just about everything I can think of! I've used a port adapter to connect it to my usb-c devices and it still works like a dream! It works with my tablet , my phone, and even my ancient laptop! I am absolutely thrilled with this keyboard. If you want something pretty, sturdy, and extra noisy, this is the one for you!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent keyboard, amazing key feedback and sound. Looks beautiful.
reviews.reviewText: This exceeded my expectations. The sound of of each key press, with the feedback is 10/10. Plenty of options for the lights, and you can tell the keyboard is made with quality parts. I ordered another for my wife. Highly recommend for the price point.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing for schoolwork
reviews.reviewText: I just started graduate school and knowing myself, I needed some fun supplies to entice me to continue with the work. This keyboard is amazing. My only complaint is hoe loud the keys are, but in very sensitive to that. I ordered a new set of switches and I'm hoping that helps. I absolutely adore the different settings for the leds, and the key caps are stunning. The keyboard makes my desk look very cool when it's just sitting there, and even cooler when I'm typing. My favorite setting is the single key glow when you press. It makes writing papers and emails extra special.EDIT: I just replaced the switches for a quieter clear tactile, and I like this keyboard infinitely better. The clickiness was getting a little annoying, and I'm very happy now with the sound and feel. I adore the look and feel of the keycaps and now I love the sound and feeling of pressing in even more. I could type all day on this thing! Half the reason I edited the review was so I'd have an excuse to type!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This keyboard is fun!
reviews.reviewText: This keyboard not only has round keys, it also makes the clickety-clackity sounds of an old fashioned typewriter. I also love how you can program the different colors to be displayed. And yes, the keyboard will go into sleep mode when you are not using it. The number keyboard on the right is spaced correctly. In the past, I purchased a keyboard and had to return it because the numbers on the right were too close together. I needed a number keyboard because I do a lot of data entry. This is a great keyboard for the price! Love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars My favorite setting quit working
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this keyboard in January 2023. I absolutely LOVE this keyboard, it adds personality to my workspace. Unfortunately my favorite setting (all keys lit up with different colors but as you hit each key that specific key changes colors) is no longer functioning. The keyboard itself works perfectly and I have enjoyed and still enjoy it. I’m just pretty bummed about the setting. 3 stars seems too low but 4 too high in my opinion and rating as a 3 was unfair.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is a must buy!
reviews.reviewText: This keyboard made me speechless. It is stunning!!!! There are so many different light settings and colors! It works perfect in my setup! The keys are just like a typewriter and are so satisfying to type on. I am beyond glad I made this purchase!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Love the sound of it. I bring it to work and use it as well as use it at home for school. There's tons of light settings, from flashing, to just flashing when typing or continuous lighting. You can adjust the type of light you want (flashing etc.) and the color. I am definitely impressed 👌

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I just LOVE this keyboard
reviews.reviewText: This brightened up my entire room! I sometimes work without lights, and this is a god-send. I can actually see the keys. AND... I just LOVE the colors!! Wish I had bought this a long time again! Seems pretty sturdy. I'm sure I'll have it for many years!!! Definitely recommend this keyboard!
